metadata.name: A Brush With Eternity V2
metadata.description:
What do we seek with our social media interactions? A viral response, instant acclaim, a taste of imortality?

What echo will ultimately remain of our posts, likes and selfies?

A collaboration between @DanishMir who created the original artwork and @Saucebook with the brushstroke animation and music.

V2 as this is a remint of the original locked in a hacked wallet.
